author: Arthur Pacaud (arthuro555)
description:
# Compressor 

If you have a big file, you might want to make it smaller, or if you have a JSON save file you might want to prevent editing it easily. 
Using the well know zip compression algorithm, you can minimify strings and restore them later with this extension.
